On Ubuntu, you need (at least) these packages:

    pstoedit
    pygmentize
    docbook2ps
    ps2pdf
    dbtoepub
    asciitosvg -> install into /usr/local/bin
    rasterizer
    inkscape

sudo apt-get install dblatex ditaa doc-base docbook docbook-dsssl docbook-utils docbook-xml docbook-xsl pstoedit perl python python-pygments docbook-utils ghostscript libbatik-java
